{{#> base}}
<h2>Event Reminder</h2>

<p>Hi {{name}},</p>

<p>This is a friendly reminder that you're registered for an upcoming event:</p>

<div class="info">
  <h3>{{eventTitle}}</h3>
  <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{eventDate}}</p>
  <p><strong>Time:</strong> {{eventTime}}</p>
  <p><strong>Location:</strong> {{eventLocation}}</p>
</div>

<p>Don't forget to arrive on time and bring any necessary items mentioned in the event details.</p>

<div style="text-align: center;">
  <a href="{{eventLink}}" class="button">View Event Details</a>
</div>

<p>We look forward to seeing you there!</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>The City Lifestyle Team</p>
{{/base}}
